  # Get QR Code
  
  Get connection QR code data for mobile app pairing. No authentication required.
  
  ## Response
  ```json
  {
    "qr": "data:image/png;base64,...",
    "connectionUrl": "http://192.168.1.100:3847/?token=xxx",
    "url": "http://192.168.1.100:3847",
    "ip": "192.168.1.100",
    "port": 3847
  }
  ```
}
